Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli kama shaidar ranar Alhamis da dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh da matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, tsarin siyasa ya ci gaba, kuma 'yan jarida sun gaji shirin sauya-sauya na ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona da FBI suka yi don gudanar da bincike mai zurfi game da zargin.
