Kamfanin ya lissafa matsakaicin masu sauraron tashoshin labarai na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox da MSNBC.
Ba a samun lambobin nan da nan a wasu cibiyoyin sadarwar da suka nuna ba, gami da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
