Sergio Aguero da Raheem Sterling sun tura mai tsaron gidan Brighton mai nasara da Manchester City ta yi 2-0 a ranar Asabar a Etihad Stadium da ke Manchester, Ingila.
Aguero ya sanya shi cikin wani ɗan wasa mai sauƙi na minti 65 na matasa.
Dan wasan Argentina ya samu nasara a wasan farko a jere.
Ya yi gwagwarmaya da masu kare hakkin Brighton uku kafin ya yi watsi da shi a filin wasa.
Daga baya Aguero ya ga cewa sun yi lalata da riguna huɗu masu launin kore.
Ya tura shi zuwa gefe ɗaya na mai karewa kafin ya sake yin wasu 'yan wasa a kusurwar akwatin Brighton.
