Ayr 38-17 Melrose: Ba tare da wuce Ayr ba, ya tashi sama
Wataƙila ƙoƙari biyu na ƙarshe sun juya sakamakon ƙarshe, amma babu shakka Ayr ya cancanci cin nasarar wannan wasan nishaɗi mai ban sha'awa na Tennent na ranar.
Kakan suna kan gaba a cikin jadawalin, kuma su ne kawai ba su wuce goma ba.
A ƙarshe, shi ne babban kariya, kamar yadda mafi yawan damar su, wanda ya kai ga gida kuma kocin Peter Murchie yana da duk haƙƙin gamsarwa.
"Mun gwada mu a bangaren wasanmu har yanzu, har yanzu ba mu da karin fitilu, don haka dole ne in yi farin ciki", in ji shi.
Robyn Christie daga Melrose ta ce: "A lokacin da ba a Ayr ba, sun yi amfani da damar su don mu yi kyau".
Gwada na Grant Anderson na minti 14, wanda ya maye gurbin Frazier Climo, ya sanya Ayr a gaba, amma, a kan katin rawaya na Scotland cap Rory Hughes, an dakatar da wasan Warriors, kuma an ba Melrose damar yin ƙididdigar lamba kuma Jason Baggot ya yi ƙoƙari ba tare da canzawa ba.
Climo ya shimfiɗa kan jagorar Ayr a cikin horo, kafin, sannan a cikin lokacinsa, ya ci kwallo kuma daga baya ya canza shi zuwa ƙoƙari na mutum don sanya 17-5 a Ayr a ƙarshen.
Amma Melrose ya fara a rabi na biyu da kyau kuma ƙoƙarin Patrick Anderson, wanda aka maye gurbin da Baggot, ya rage 'yancinsa da maki biyar.
Daga bisani an sami tsire-tsire na jiran rauni mai tsanani na Ruarid Knott, wanda aka cire, kuma a farkon, Ayr ya ƙara haɗuwa da kai har zuwa ƙoƙarin Stafford McDowall, wanda aka maye gurbin da Climo.
Wakilin Kyaftin Ayr, Blair Macpherson daga baya an ba shi katin rawaya, kuma a wannan lokacin, Melrose ya yi ƙarin biyan kuɗi tare da ƙoƙarin Bruce Colvine wanda ba a canza shi ba, wanda ya ƙare da mummunan matsin lamba.
Komawa gida, duk da haka, kuma lokacin da aka ba Struan Hutchinson rawaya don ƙarfafa Climo ba tare da ball ba, farawa da horo na waje, MacPherson ya taɓa baya kuma rauni Ayr ya ci gaba.
Climo ya canza, kamar yadda ya yi a sake farawa, bayan Kyle Rowe wanda ya kawo ragowar akwatin da David Armstrong ya kawo masa aka aika shi zuwa Gregor Henry mai daraja a waje da ƙoƙari na biyar na gefen gidan.
Tauraruwar Still Game tana kama da sabon aiki a masana'antar cin abinci.
Tauraron wasan Still Game Ford Kieran yana neman wani ɓangare na masana'antar maraba lokacin da aka gano cewa an nada shi a matsayin darektan kamfanin gidan cin abinci mai lasisi.
Dan shekara 56 ya taka rawa a cikin shahararren wasan kwaikwayo na BBC, Jack Jarvis, wanda ya rubuta kuma ya yi aiki tare da tauraron mai sha'awar nishaɗi na dogon lokaci Greg Hemphill.
An sanar da cewa jerin na tara na gaba zai zama na ƙarshe na wasan kwaikwayon, kuma ga alama Kiernan yana shirin rayuwa bayan Craiglang.
A cewar bayanan da aka rubuta a cikin kundin tsarin mulki, shi ne darektan Adriftmorn Limited.
Wakilin ya ƙi yin sharhi game da labarin, kuma a cikin wata majiya ta Scottish Sun ta nuna cewa Kiernan yana neman ku shiga cikin "kasuwancin gidan abinci mai girma" na Glasgow.
'Teku ne Mu': Ƙasar Bolivia ba ta da teku tana fatan kotu ta sake buɗe hanyar Pacific
Sailors na jirgin ruwa a cikin tashoshin rigging-clad na Sojojin Ruwa a La Paz.
Gidajen jama'a suna yin yawo a kan tutar teku.
A wani takarda da suka yi a sansanin sojojin ruwa na Lake Titicaca a Amazon, sun rubuta cewa: "Teku ne teku a matsayinmu na doka.
Dole ne a san shi".
A lokacin da ƙasar Bolivia ba ta da teku, ƙwaƙwalwar bakin teku a Chile ta kasance mai ƙarfi a cikin rikici mai zubar da jini na ƙarni na 19 - kamar yadda yake a cikin tunanin bayyana Tekun Fasifik a wani lokaci.
Wannan fata ce mafi girma a cikin shekaru goma, kamar yadda Bolivia ke jiran hukuncin kotun shari'a ta duniya a ranar 1 ga Oktoba bayan shekaru biyar na shawarwari.
"Bolivia tana da haɗin kai, ruhun haɗin kai da haɗin kai, kuma tabbas tana tsammanin kyakkyawan sakamako", in ji Roberto Calzadilla, masanin harkokin wajen ƙasar Bolivia.
Yawancin 'yan Bolivia suna kallon hukuncin ICJ a manyan allon ƙasa, kamar yadda kotun Hague ke ganin ya dace da ikirarin Bolivia cewa - bayan shekaru da yawa na tattaunawa - Chile ta tilasta ta tattauna game da ba da Bolivia's 'yancin fita daga teku.
Evo Morales, shugaban kasa na Bolivia mai jan hankali - wanda ke fuskantar rikici mai rikitarwa don sake zaɓe a shekara mai zuwa - yana da babban matsayi a kan mulki a ranar Litinin.
"Muna kusa da komawa zuwa Tekun Fasifik", ya yi alkawarin a ƙarshen Agusta.
Amma wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa kotu ba za ta iya yanke hukunci ba game da Bolivia - kuma cewa zai canza kadan idan ta yi.
Kungiyar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da ke Netherlands ba ta da ikon bayar da wani abu a ƙasar Chile, kuma ta ce ba ta yanke shawarar sakamakon yiwuwar tattaunawa ba.
A cewar Paz Zárate, masanin shari'ar duniya na Chile, hukuncin da kotun ICJ ta yanke zai zo ne bayan watanni shida da aka yi sauraron muhawara ta karshe da ta bayyana cewa shari'ar "ba ta da ƙarfi".
Kuma ba tare da yin nisa da abin da ya sa Bolivia ba, shekaru hudu da suka gabata za su iya jinkirta.
"Suna daukan matakin samun damar shiga teku daga gwamnatin Bolivia ta yanzu", in ji Zárate.
Ta ce, jawabin Morales na nuna rashin son kai ya rage a cikin sha'awar 'yan Chile.
Bolivia da Chile suna ci gaba da magana game da shi, kuma yana da wuya a yi tattaunawa bayan wannan.
Tun daga shekarar 1962 kasashen biyu ba su musanya wakilan ba.
Tsohon shugaban kasa Eduardo Rodríguez Veltzé, wakilin Bolivia a Hague, ya ƙi yarda da ra'ayin cewa yanke shawara a kotun ba zai yi sauri ba.
Ya ce Litinin zai ba Bolivia " dama ta musamman ta bude sabuwar zamanin sadarwa a Chile " da kuma damar "karshen shekaru 139 na rikice-rikice na amfanin juna", ya ce.
Calzadilla ya kuma musanta cewa Morales - wanda har yanzu shine shugaban kasar Latin Amurka mafi shahara - ya yi amfani da batun teku a matsayin hanyar siyasa.
Ya kara da cewa, "Bolivia ba ta taba yin watsi da hakkinta na samun tekun Pacific ba".
