Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa kwamitin duniya a Babban Taron shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki muhimman matakai masu kyau a bara, kamar dakatar da gwajin nukiliya, raba wurin gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin kada ta yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
"Amma ba mu ga wani amsa mai dacewa daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
