Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ta afkawa babban birnin Indonesia Palu a ranar Juma'a, jami'an sun ce, yayin da ake sa ran mutuwar za ta karu.
Da yake an katse sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun bayanai a yankin Donggala Regency ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu kusa da wurin girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
A babban birnin Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 a lokacin bala'in.
Ga wasu mahimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke kusa da bakin teku mai bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a kimanin 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala yanki ne mai iyaka wanda ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) a gabar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gwamnatin, wani yanki na gudanarwa a jihar, tana da kimanin mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Fishing da noma sune manyan abubuwan tattalin arziki na yankin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a bakin tekun Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a yankin, amma galibi suna da yawa a Morowali, gabar tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, Palu da Donggala sun sami tsunami sau da yawa, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekarar 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane sama da 200 kuma ya lalata daruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Sunami ya kuma afkawa yankin yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yanayin girgizar ƙasa da guguwar Volcanoes a Tekun Fasifik kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa akai-akai.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar yamma ta lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya addabi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai nauyin 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami a gabar kudu, inda ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai nauyin 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin jihar Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai, a wajen Sumatra, ta haddasa tsunami mai tsayi na mita 10, wanda ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai dauke da makamai ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, wanda ya haifar da rushewa da firgici yayin da mutane suka tuna da girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu tsunami da aka yi a wannan lokacin, amma fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mafi girma ta afkawa tsibirin yawon bude ido na Indonesia Lombok, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a keɓewar wucin gadi.
