Syria ta ce tana shirye ta dauki 'yan gudun hijira da son rai kuma tana neman taimako wajen mayar da kasar da ta lalace a cikin yakin da ya shafe shekaru sama da bakwai.
A jawabinsa a taron jam'iyyar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya ce suna duba halin da kasar ke ciki.
"Yanzu yanayin ƙasa ya fi kwanciyar hankali da aminci wanda ya haifar da ci gaba a cikin yaƙi da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gano wuraren da ta'addanci ya lalata domin inganta zaman lafiya.
Dukkanin yanayi suna shirya 'yan gudun hijira su koma ƙasar da suka gudu daga ta'addanci da kuma matakan duniya da ke mayar da hankali kan rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 sun bar kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya fara a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar suna bukatar taimakon agaji.
Al-Moualem ya ce yana neman taimakon gwamnatin Siriya don sake gina kasar da ta rushe.
Amma ya nace cewa ba za su yarda da taimakon da ake bukata ba ko kuma daga kasashen da ke tallafawa ta'addanci.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a birnin Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 ta hanyar lashe gasar Amurka da jimlar jimla daga 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a wajen birnin Paris, Faransa.
A yanzu haka ne karo na shida da Amurka ta yi nasara a kan wani yanki na Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun nasara lokacin da kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya kai maki 14.5 da ya buƙaci don ya doke Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda bai yi wasa mai kyau a gasar cin kofin duniya ba, ya jefa tasa a cikin ruwa a cikin rami na 16 na par-3, kuma wasan ya sami Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan golf na Italiya ya ci dukkan wasanninsa, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa biyar da suka taba samun ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar ta yanzu a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya sanya dan wasan Turai mafi ƙasƙanci a cikin 5 & 4, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan duniya Dustin Johnson ya fadi 2 da 1 a kan Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai buga wasan karshe.
A gasar cin kofin Ryder, dan wasan Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi yawan maki tare da maki 25.5 a lokacin wasan.
